snippet.title: MLB The Show 23 - Legends Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/mlb-the-show/

Derek Jeter, David Wright, Sammy Sosa, Mark McGwire, and many more including legends from the Negro Leagues! MLB The Show 23 has more than 180 Legends for you to find and create a dominating squad. Get Early Access beginning March 24, 2023 with the Digital Deluxe Edition or The Captain Edition. MLB The Show 23 is available March 28, 2023. #MLBTheShow #owntheshow
